      %li=link_to "Rare Book & Manuscript Library", "https://library.columbia.edu/libraries/rbml.html"

    %p{:style => "font-size: 16px;"} Archival collections include personal papers, institutional records, corporate archives, architectural drawings, oral histories, printed ephemera, objects, and more.
    %p{:style => "font-size: 16px;"} CLIO searches collection-level descriptions only.
    %p{:style => "font-size: 16px;"} To search the full text of the associated finding aids, try #{link_to 'Archival Finding Aids', 'https://findingaids.library.columbia.edu/'}.
    %p{:style => "font-size: 16px;"} To search for digital content, try #{link_to 'Digital Library Collections', 'https://dlc.library.columbia.edu/'}.





